      "content": "i know... i've thought about talking to someone but it feels like even a doctor or a counselor would just see me as another problem to solve. like, even if i talk to a professional, the yelling and the comments won't just stop. it feels like the only way to actually get some silence is to just... not be here. to just stop existing so the noise finally goes away. does that even make sense or am i just crazy?",
